column3: Status associated with the Privacy Negotiation
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation is completed and the parties have accepted the relevant terms
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation is completed and the parties have refused the relevant terms
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation process has been initiated
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation has been requested to be initiated
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation has been refused to be initiated or continued
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation process is underway and is awaiting a response from the other party
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation has been paused i.e. halted or put on hold without a specific decision
Status indicating the terms involved in Privacy Negotiation were not accepted and a counter-offer has been made with a different set of terms
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation is deemed to be invalid and therefore cannot continue
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation has been terminated by one or more parties
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation has expired due to inactivity by a party or due to other reasons
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation requires a confirmation by a human before it can proceed
Status indicating the state of Privacy Negotiation is unknown
Status indicating the Privacy Negotiation requires a clarification from the other party regarding the relevant context
